1.0-beta-2
    - Only copy EXIF tags to extracted JPEG to avoid timezone issues.
    - Reworked project layout to use ExtUtils::MakeMaker replacing build.sh.
    - New option: --include to control which files are processed
    - New option: --exclude to control which files should not be processed
    - New option: --config to allow options to be specified in a file

1.0-beta-1
    - Initial release
